---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../../utils/constants';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Training Services - ${SITE_CONFIG.title}`}
  description="Ethical, people-first training programs in Data Science and Analytics. Transform careers through integrity, mentorship, and real-world impact."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-gray-900 to-black text-white py-20 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, transparent, transparent 12px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 12px, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 24px);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-yellow-400/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-yellow-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-yellow-400/30 bg-yellow-400/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-yellow-400 mb-6">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 animate-pulse"></span>
          Training Services
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight md:whitespace-nowrap">
          The Corpnce <span class="text-yellow-400">Ethical Compass</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          A Foundation of Integrity
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-20">
      
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-yellow-400 to-yellow-600 rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="pl-8">
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light">
            At Corpnce, our approach to training is rooted in the belief that technology—however advanced—is a human tool that must serve human ends. We view the education of Data Scientists and Analysts not merely as a transfer of technical skills, but as a commitment to the long-term prosperity and dignity of our students and the society they will impact.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section I: Ethical Core -->
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-yellow-50/30 to-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-yellow-100/50 rounded-full blur-3xl -mr-32 -mt-32"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-black">I</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-black">Our Ethical Core: Principles over Profits</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            We operate on a <strong class="text-black font-bold">"People-First"</strong> business model. In an industry often characterized by aggressive sales and mass-batching, we uphold four fundamental ethical pillars:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-yellow-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a2 2 0 012-2h4.586A2 2 0 0112 2.586L15.414 6A2 2 0 0116 7.414V16a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 mt-2">Radical Transparency</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We provide honest assessments of market demand and candidate readiness. We do not overpromise "guaranteed" outcomes; instead, we promise the guaranteed quality of mentorship required to achieve them.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-yellow-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM17 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM12.93 17c.046-.327.07-.66.07-1a6.97 6.97 0 00-1.5-4.33A5 5 0 0119 16v1h-6.07zM6 11a5 5 0 015 5v1H1v-1a5 5 0 015-5z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 mt-2">The Mentorship Covenant</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                By strictly limiting batches to 15 students, we ensure that no learner is treated as a statistic. Every student is a unique professional journey that deserves direct, personalized attention.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-yellow-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 mt-2">Equitable Access</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We believe elite tech education should not be a privilege of the few. By pricing our programs at a fraction of global executive costs, we lower the barriers to entry for talented individuals from all backgrounds.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-yellow-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 mt-2">Intellectual Honesty</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We teach our students to respect the data. In our curriculum, "Ethics in AI" is not an elective; it is woven into every module—from addressing algorithmic bias to ensuring data privacy and transparency.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section II: Responsibility to Student -->
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-amber-50/20 to-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-amber-100/50 rounded-full blur-3xl -ml-32 -mb-32"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">II</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-black">Our Responsibility to the Student</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Our ethical obligation extends beyond the classroom. We view the enrollment of a student as a trust-based partnership:
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500"></span>
                Sustainable Skill-Building
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We avoid "shortcut" learning. We teach the rigorous mathematical and logical foundations that allow a professional to adapt as tools change, ensuring their career is built on stone, not sand.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500"></span>
                Professional Advocacy
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Our placement assistance is an act of advocacy. We don't just "push" resumes; we match the right talent with the right culture, ensuring a mutually beneficial relationship between our graduates and their future employers.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500"></span>
                The "Bridge" Internship
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We take responsibility for the "Experience Gap." By providing internal internships on real-world products, we ensure students don't face the "no job without experience/no experience without a job" paradox.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section III: Responsibility to Society -->
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-emerald-50/20 to-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-100/50 rounded-full blur-3xl -ml-32 -mt-32"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">III</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-black">Our Responsibility to Society</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            As a training vertical based in India's tech capital, we acknowledge our role in shaping the nation's digital future:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-emerald-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-3">Bias Mitigation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                We train our students to be the "conscience" of the companies they join. They are taught to identify and rectify biases in datasets that could lead to unfair social or economic outcomes.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-emerald-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-3">Socially Conscious Data Use</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                We advocate for the use of Data Science and AI to solve real-world problems—be it in healthcare, environmental sustainability, or financial inclusion.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-emerald-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black mb-3">Lifelong Support</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Our commitment doesn't end with a certificate. We provide lifetime access to our community, serving as a permanent resource for our alumni as they navigate the ethical dilemmas of the modern workplace.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Quote Section -->
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-gray-900 to-black p-10 md:p-16 text-white border-2 border-yellow-400/30">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-yellow-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -mr-48 -mt-48"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="text-6xl font-black text-yellow-400/30 mb-4">"</div>
          <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
            At Corpnce, success is not measured by the number of certificates we issue, but by the integrity and impact of the professionals we produce. We don't just train people to code; we train them to care about what their code does to the world.
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Second Main Section: Engineering Professional Transitions -->
      <section class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-500 to-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="pl-8">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-6 leading-tight">
            Engineering Professional <span class="text-yellow-500">Transitions</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            At Corpnce, we don't just teach technology; we engineer professional transitions. In an era where AI agents and automated analytics are redefining the value of human labor, we provide the architectural blueprint for the next generation of tech leaders.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            Based in the heart of <strong class="text-black">Rajajinagar, Bangalore</strong>, we operate at the intersection of Industrial Demand and Academic Excellence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Philosophy Section -->
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-blue-50/20 to-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-100/50 rounded-full blur-3xl -mr-32 -mt-32"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">I</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-black">Our Philosophy: The "Simplicity-to-Scale" Framework</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            We believe that complexity is the enemy of execution. Our business model is built on an abstract three-layer transformation:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black mb-4">1</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Deconstruction</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We strip away the jargon of Data Science and Analytics, rebuilding your foundational logic in Python and SQL.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black mb-4">2</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Synthesis</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We integrate traditional statistical rigor with 2026-frontier tools—Generative AI, Agentic workflows, and Cloud-native BI.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-blue-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black mb-4">3</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Validation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We shift the focus from "Learning hours" to "Production outputs." Your success is measured by the GitHub repository you build, not the hours you sit in a chair.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Dual-Vertical Specialization -->
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-purple-50/20 to-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-100/50 rounded-full blur-3xl -ml-32 -mb-32"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">II</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-black">The Dual-Vertical Specialization</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            We focus exclusively on two high-impact domains where the talent gap is most acute in 2026:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-purple-300 p-8 hover:border-purple-500 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-black">I</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-black">Program I: Masters in Machine Learning & AI Agents</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Target</p>
                  <p class="text-lg font-bold text-black">The Architects of Automation</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Focus</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Building self-reasoning agents, deploying MLOps pipelines, and mastering Deep Learning.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Outcome</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Transitioning from a coder to an AI Architect capable of implementing research-level breakthroughs.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-purple-300 p-8 hover:border-purple-500 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-black">II</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-black">Program II: Advanced Masters in AI & Data Architecture</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Target</p>
                  <p class="text-lg font-bold text-black">The Decision Strategists</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Focus</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Real-time diagnostic analytics, AI-augmented visualization (Power BI/Tableau Pulse), and Predictive Modeling.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Outcome</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Becoming a Decision Scientist who turns petabytes of raw data into billion-dollar business strategies.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Elite Hub Business Model -->
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-yellow-50/40 to-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-yellow-100/50 rounded-full blur-3xl -ml-32 -mt-32"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-yellow-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-black">III</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-black">The Corpnce "Elite Hub" Business Model</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            We differentiate our training business through three non-negotiable pillars:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-yellow-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-yellow-500 text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black mb-4">15</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">The 15-Student Limit</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We prioritize Batch Quality over Volume. By limiting intake to 15 students, we ensure a boutique, high-touch mentorship environment that larger institutes cannot replicate.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-yellow-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-yellow-500 text-black flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 2a1 1 0 000 2h2a1 1 0 100-2H9z"/>
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 5a2 2 0 012-2 3 3 0 003 3h2a3 3 0 003-3 2 2 0 012 2v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V5zm9.707 5.707a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 12.586l-1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">The Internship Ecosystem</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We bridge the "Experience Gap" by integrating top performers into our internal AI product development cycles. You don't just study for the industry; you work within it.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-yellow-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-yellow-500 text-black flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black mb-4">1/4</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Economic Transparency</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                We provide "Tier-1 Elite Training" at a 1/4th price point of global executive programs. Our ROI-first approach ensures that your first salary jump often covers your entire course fee.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

